scene.message:
Yukino: We suddenly popped{nl}
out somewhere weird.{nl}
What's this skeleton room?{waitkey}{ret}

???: Yoo-hoo!{nl}
Everyoooone!{nl}
Niiice to meet you!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Welcooome to my domain,{nl}
the "Tower of Thanatos"!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Everybody!{nl}
Are you fiiired uuup?!{nl}
Everyone's idol,{waitkey}{clearbox}"Yuriko Yamamoto"-chan,{nl}
heeere!!{nl}
Nice to meetcha!!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: What kind of joke{nl}
is this??{waitkey}{clearbox}It may not be my place, but{nl}
please use proper Japanese.{nl}
It's truly unpleasant.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Yeeeah!!{nl}
Y!{wait_fr:30} U!{wait_fr:30} R!{wait_fr:30} I!{wait_fr:30} K!{wait_fr:30} O!{nl}
Yuri-{wait_fr:30}koooo!{waitkey}{clearbox}...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...wait, no.{nl}
Hey, what gives?! You got{nl}
me all hyped up for nothing!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: What? This dumb-{nl}
looking girl. And she talks{nl}
weird too.{waitkey}{clearbox}You're, like, super weird!{waitkey}{ret}

Yuriko: Geez, what?!{nl}
This weird girl!?{nl}
Ahh, Yuriko's so cute you're{waitkey}jealous, maybe!?{waitkey}{clearbox}Being too cute is a{nl}
c-{wait_fr:30}rime{wait_fr:30}, y'know!{waitkey}{clearbox}Sorry for being{nl}
too adorable!{nl}
Kyahahahaha!!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: ...{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30}...What!?{nl}
What did you come out for?!{nl}
We're in a hurry!{waitkey}{clearbox}So?{wait_fr:30} Do you mean to have{nl}
a fight here? We're perfectly{nl}
fine with that!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Oh...{wait_fr:30} No...{nl}
What did you come out for?{waitkey}{clearbox}Do you mean to fight us here?{nl}
We don't mind in the least,{nl}
you know?{waitkey}{ret}

Yuriko: Geez, don't say such{nl}
scary things, no no!{nl}
I'm just gonna teach you how{waitkey}to open the door in back!{waitkey}{clearbox}So listen up - Yuriko-chan's{nl}
door-opening lesson! ...or{nl}
something!{waitkey}{clearbox}Y'see, there are two candles,{nl}
one on each side of the door,{nl}
right?{waitkey}{clearbox}Snuff out either one's flame{nl}
and the door opens!{waitkey}{clearbox}So do your best and come to{nl}
me! Bye-bye!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Somehow... no matter{nl}
how I think about it, this{nl}
reeks of a trap.{waitkey}{clearbox}Still, she might be a pretty{nl}
tricky opponent, that{nl}
Yuriko...{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Somehow this tower's{nl}
air feels creepy. I can't{nl}
quite put it into words...{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Damn it! We got got!!{waitkey}{clearbox}That Yuriko woman! She looks{nl}
dumb, but she's a real{nl}
piece of work!{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: What's with that{nl}
dumb-looking girl? She's,{nl}
like, super mocking life!{waitkey}Like!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Like she's totally making{nl}
fun of people!! Something{nl}
about her ticks me off!!{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Honestly... one{nl}
noisy Ayase is more than{nl}
enough as it is...{waitkey}{clearbox}With even the enemy boss{nl}
like that, I dread what's{nl}
ahead.{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: Hey, hey, just between{nl}
us... that Yuriko-chan was{nl}
pretty cute, huh!!{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: What's scary about that{nl}
Yuriko woman is you can't{nl}
tell what she's thinking...{waitkey}{clearbox}It's as if she's enjoying{nl}
battling us, enjoying{nl}
trapping us...{waitkey}{clearbox}As Yukino says, she seems an{nl}
opponent who won't fall to{nl}
a straightforward approach.{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Ngh?!{nl}
Wh...{wait_fr:30}what...{wait_fr:30}is this?{nl}
Something's draining{waitkey}out of my body...{waitkey}{clearbox}Gwaah!!{nl}
Aaaaah!!{waitkey}{ret}

Yuriko: Ha-ha! Gotcha! Gotcha!{nl}
Kyahahahaha!{waitkey}Thought you could pass for{nl}
free?!{waitkey}{clearbox}Life is "give and take"!{nl}
Want to do something in this{nl}
tower? Then you gotta give{waitkey}{clearbox}Yuriko-chan something!{nl}
No good!{waitkey}{clearbox}Life is harsh, y'know!{nl}
So, I've definitely taken{nl}
your other self's life,{waitkey}your Per-{wait_fr:30}so-{wait_fr:30}na{wait_fr:30}, sure did!{waitkey}{clearbox}Buh-byeee!{nl}
Kyahahahaha!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: Damn it! What the{nl}
heck?! That woman!!{waitkey}{clearbox}What's this? "I've taken{nl}
your other self's life"?{nl}
What does that mean?{waitkey}{ret}

Yuriko: Ha-ha! Gotcha! Gotcha!{nl}
Kyahahahaha!{waitkey}Thought you could pass for{nl}
free?!{waitkey}{clearbox}Life is "give and take"!{nl}
Want to do something in this{nl}
tower? Then you gotta give{waitkey}{clearbox}Yuriko-chan something!{nl}
No good!{waitkey}{clearbox}Life is harsh, y'know!{nl}
So, I've definitely taken{nl}
your other self's life,{waitkey}your Per-{wait_fr:30}so-{wait_fr:30}na{wait_fr:30}, sure did!{waitkey}{clearbox}Buh-byeee!{nl}
Kyahahahaha!{waitkey}{ret}

It seems the door won't open{nl}
unless you snuff out one{nl}
of the candles.{waitkey}{ret}
